From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: MC20018 <winme2001@outlook.com>
Date: Mon, 8 Jun 2026 16:15:22 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Complete ecosystem event hooks

Add vanilla hook points for the remaining high-value ecosystem events, including detailed portal, hopper, potion, leash, shearing, fishing, entity item transfer, entity block-change, damage-by-entity, piston push, cauldron, sponge, fertilize, fluid, and brewing stand fuel behavior.

Keep patched Minecraft code thin by routing event construction, cancellation semantics, mutable payload application, and listener failure handling through Fand bridge helpers.

